"""
CallCare — HTTP Evidence via OpenAI web_search (Python 3.9 safe)

Scalable behavior only:
- Extract URLs from web_search_call.action.sources (NOT results).
- Block PubMed/PMC/NCBI.
- Fetch <title> for stable citations.
- Diversity cap (max_per_publisher, default 2).
- Generic relevance filter:
    derive keywords from clinical anchor text (assessment_text preferred),
    keep sources with >=N keyword hits in title+url.
- Generic query templates only (NO condition/anatomy hardcoding).
- Evidence formatting:
  TITLE. PUBLISHER. URL. Accessed YYYY-MM-DD.
"""

